法院是否有管轄權？甲未將丙列為被告，關於本案件之當事人適格問
題，法院應如何處理？（30分）', '[]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:26:27+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "2fb11834bf6a", "answer_pdf_sha1": null, "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "114120", "c": "101", "s": "0406", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "甲、申論題部分", "subject": "民事訴訟法", "year": "114", "exam_name": "114年公務人員特種考試司法人員考試、法務部調查局調查人員考試、海岸巡防人員考試、未具擬任職務任用資格取得法官遴選資格考試", "original_question_number": "一", "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "judicial", "civil_category": "公證人"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('judicial-4d3895b1-moex-00014', 'judicial-4d3895b1', 'judicial-4d3895b1-moex-114-4bf6d96a', 'sub-judicial-4d3895b1-04', NULL, 'essay', '原告甲起訴請求被告乙給付買賣價金新臺幣（下同）200 萬元；乙抗辯
